WEBVTT

00:01.423 --> 00:03.324
I have a bit of an
announcement to make!

00:03.392 --> 00:06.660
My blog is going to be published
as a book.

00:06.728 --> 00:07.895
That's great, Lou.

00:07.929 --> 00:09.329
<i>Send us your favourite entries</i>

00:09.364 --> 00:10.697
and I'll get them
to my publisher.

00:10.766 --> 00:12.332
<i>And if you could do that</i>
<i>sooner rather than later,</i>

00:12.400 --> 00:13.567
that'd be great,

00:13.635 --> 00:14.802
because we're already organizing
a book tour.

00:14.870 --> 00:17.838
A... a book tour?!
Okay!

00:17.906 --> 00:19.173
Goodbye!

00:19.207 --> 00:21.608
Not goodbye.

00:21.643 --> 00:25.512
Just... till next time.

00:25.580 --> 00:27.281
Okay, till next time.

00:32.987 --> 00:34.588
It's okay, Spartan.
It's okay, it's okay!

00:34.622 --> 00:35.989
It's just a thunderstorm.

00:36.056 --> 00:37.456
You're fine, you're fine!

00:37.524 --> 00:38.992
I know, I'm right here.

00:39.059 --> 00:41.560
I'm right here.
Good boy!

00:41.628 --> 00:43.562
Amy, take care of this guy!

00:43.630 --> 00:45.165
Sure. How are the other horses?

00:45.232 --> 00:47.466
Well, it's not
their first storm,

00:47.534 --> 00:49.635
but this one's
a little spooked!

00:49.670 --> 00:51.104
<i>Easy...</i>

00:51.172 --> 00:52.438
Nothing's gonna hurt you!

00:53.940 --> 00:56.642
<i>Whoa!</i>
<i>That was close!</i>

00:56.710 --> 00:58.744
Yeah, too close!

01:00.180 --> 01:01.580
I got him.

01:03.000 --> 01:09.074
